snippet.title: RTGame
snippet.description:
Hi I'm an Irish Guy that plays games. Enjoy my content, or else.

All of my videos are edited livestream highlights taken from my Twitch channel. My stream schedule is: 
~Tuesday & Thursday @ 7pm 
~Saturday & Sunday @ 3pm 
All times based in Ireland. 

For stream notifications, follow my Twitch channel, Twitter and Discord Server!
Icon and art assets made by Akialyne. She's a smelly nerd: https://twitter.com/akialyne
